<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kelola Antrian - Admin</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="admin-container">
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-header">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-university"></i> Admin Panel</h3>
            </div>
            <nav class="sidebar-nav">
                <a href="/admin/dashboard"><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i> Dashboard</a>
                <a href="/admin/queues" class="active"><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Kelola Antrian</a>
                <a href="/admin/videos"><i class="fas fa-video"></i> Kelola Video</a>
                <a href="/admin/settings"><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> Pengaturan</a>
                <a href="/admin/logout"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> Logout</a>
            </nav>
        </aside>

        <main class="main-content">
            <header class="main-header">
                <h1>Kelola Antrian</h1>
                <p>Opsi untuk mengatur ulang sistem antrian.</p>
            </header>
            
            <div class="content-body">
                <section class="quick-actions">
                    <h3>Reset Antrian</h3>
                    <p>Gunakan tombol ini untuk menghapus semua data antrian hari ini dan memulai dari awal. Aksi ini tidak dapat dibatalkan.</p>
                    <div class="action-buttons">
                        <button id="reset-queues-btn" class="btn btn-danger">
                            <i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i> Reset Semua Antrian
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/admin.js"></script>
</body>
</html>